<p><a href="https://docs.pola.rs/api/rust/dev/polars/prelude/struct.LazyCsvReader.html"><span class="twemoji"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 7H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v8h2v-4h2v4h2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m0 4H5V9h2m7-2h-4v10h2v-4h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m0 4h-2V9h2m6 0v6h1v2h-4v-2h1V9h-1V7h4v2Z"></path></svg></span>  <code>LazyCsvReader</code></a><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">·</font></font><a href="https://docs.pola.rs/api/rust/dev/polars_lazy/frame/struct.LazyFrame.html#method.filter"><span class="twemoji"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 7H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v8h2v-4h2v4h2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m0 4H5V9h2m7-2h-4v10h2v-4h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m0 4h-2V9h2m6 0v6h1v2h-4v-2h1V9h-1V7h4v2Z"></path></svg></span>  <code>filter</code></a><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">·</font></font><a href="https://docs.pola.rs/api/rust/dev/polars_lazy/frame/struct.LazyFrame.html#method.group_by"><span class="twemoji"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 7H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v8h2v-4h2v4h2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m0 4H5V9h2m7-2h-4v10h2v-4h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m0 4h-2V9h2m6 0v6h1v2h-4v-2h1V9h-1V7h4v2Z"></path></svg></span>  <code>group_by</code></a><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">·</font></font><a href="https://docs.pola.rs/api/rust/dev/polars/prelude/struct.LazyFrame.html#method.collect"><span class="twemoji"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 7H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v8h2v-4h2v4h2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m0 4H5V9h2m7-2h-4v10h2v-4h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m0 4h-2V9h2m6 0v6h1v2h-4v-2h1V9h-1V7h4v2Z"></path></svg></span>  <code>collect</code></a><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">·</font></font><a class